*Srećni* ljudi su se smejali. (The happy people were laughing.)

Gledali smo *srećne* porodice. (We watched happy families.)

Oni su bili *srećni*, kada su se sreli. (They were happy when they met.)

Ovi ljudi su se veselili *sreći*. (These people were rejoicing in happiness.)

Oni su se radovali *sreći*. (They were rejoicing in happiness.)

Ona je bila potpuno *srećna*. (She was completely happy.)